    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with the dual-VANOS system recently overhauled and rod bearings replaced with coated shells for long-term reliability. The chassis integrity is preserved via professional rear subframe reinforcement. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension retains its factory-spec kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the signature telepathic steering response. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the finish exhibits zero orange peel or clear coat failure, and the interior bolsters show no compression or dye wear. This is a turn",
