      "description": "Presented in true showroom condition, this vehicle is an impeccable example of pride in ownership. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the alloy wheels are untouched by curb rash. Inside, the cabin still carries that distinct new-car aroma; the premium leather seats are firm with no bolster wear or creasing, and the high-gloss trim is devoid of any scratches. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and comes with a comprehensive folder of every service record from day one. The engine bay is detailed to a professional standard, and the car drives with the tightness and precision of a vehicle that just rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare, investment-grade find for a buyer who demands perfection.",
